data.title: William Pickett Williamson
data.text:
Birth - Marriage - Death - Burial

Birth*17 July 1903Â William Pickett Williamson was born on 17 July 1903 at South Carolina, USA.1Â Marriage*28 January 1933Â He, at age 29 years, 6 months and 11 days married Vester Elizabeth Graham at age 22 years, 1 month and 9 days on 28 January 1933 at Danville, Pittsylvania County, Virginia, USA...2

Â Death*31 May 1958Â William Pickett Williamson died on 31 May 1958 at Shawboro, Currituck County, North Carolina, USA, at age 54 years, 10 months and 14 days.3

Â Burial*2 June 1958Â He was buried on 2 June 1958 at West Lawn Memorial Park Cemetery, Elizabeth City, Pasquotank County, North Carolina, USA .
